Feature: Manage Squadrons
  In order to divide large numbers of ships into more manageable units
  As an commander in chief of a given side
  I need to be able to create, delete, and update squadrons, and move ships between them 

  @wip
  Scenario: Admirals and Ship Captains may not manage squadrons

  @wip
  Scenario: Unregistered Users may not manage squadrons

  @wip
  Scenario: Commanders in Chief may add new squadrons to their own side

  @wip
  Scenario: Commanders in Chief may update friendly squadron names
 
  @wip
  Scenario: Commanders in Chief may move ships between friendly squadrons

  @wip
  Scenario: Commanders in Chief may reorder ships within squadrons

  @wip
  Scenario: Commanders in Chief may delete empty squadrons

  @wip
  Scenario: The last squadron on a side cannot be deleted

